R. Grodecki, believes that the principle of the Seniorate was established by Zbigniew. R. Grodecki, S. Zachorowski, J. D&lt;U+0105&gt;browski: Dzieje Polski &lt;U+015B&gt;redniowiecznej, vol. I, pp. 135-136. Another view was showed by G. Labuda, which indicates that Zbigniew not considered the Seniorate concept, and only applied the principle of equality since 1102. G. Labuda: Korona i infu&lt;U+0142&gt;a. Od monarchii do poliarchii, Krak&lt;U+00F3&gt;w 1996, pp. 16-17, ISBN 83-03-03659-9.↩
